index.title: Almost Actors
index.description: Almost Actors is a comedic webseries based on the terrible and often hysterical archetypes you meet in acting school, created by Tiarra Sulyk, Athena Russell, and Jessica McLeod.
index.writtenBy: Tiarra Sulyk, Athena Russell, & Jessica McLeod
index.starring: Athena Russell, Tiarra Sulyk, Ben Groulx, Meaghan Hommy, Jessica McLeod, Cody Wilson, Robyn Westcott, Mark Anthony Parinas, Matt Mazur, Julian LeBlanc, Nicholas Carella
